Features
</Paragraph>

            <Paragraph>Accumulation Distribution is a weighted sum of the volume values, with the weight determined by where the closing price is in relation to the days high and low price. If the closing price is closer to the days high, then the weight is positive. If the closing price is closer to the days low, then the weight is negative.</Paragraph>
        

